name: Fitting
shortdesc: Options for fitting content to a frame.

property.name: PROPORTIONAL
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fit the frame while preserving content proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some empty space occurs in the frame.

property.name: FIT_CONTENT_TO_FRAME
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fit the frame. Note: Content that is a different size than the frame appears stretched or squeezed.

property.name: FIT_FRAME_TO_CONTENT
property.shortdesc: Resizes the frame to fit the content.

property.name: PRESERVE_SIZES
property.shortdesc: Preserves the original sizes of the frame and the content. Note: Content that is larger than the frame is obscured around the edges.

property.name: FILL_PROPORTIONAL
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fill the frame while preserving content proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some content is obscured by the bounding box of the frame.
